{"tid":2441593,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"中原CSI連升11周共21.62點 預示樓價穩步上升","createTime":"2021-03-10T20:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T02:12:47.000Z","uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"392b18103002835e552c9e71a176d09357a61eec","tid":2441593,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:59:30.000Z","msg":"CSI連升至今11周，是2019年4月以來<strong><span class=\"red\">最長的連升</span></strong>。當時CSI連升15周，由40.23點升至81.43點，累計升幅達41.20點。同期樓價尋底成功，兼重拾升軌，CCL累升8.1%。CSI現時連升11周，順利升穿45點至55點好淡分界區間，確認樓價不會掉頭回落。但今次升勢更為緩慢，相信連升周數有機會打破15周水平，預示樓價升勢更為温和而漫長。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2897532/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2897532%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=425b4bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2897532/</a>"},{"pid":"b9ee7125e4fcacbb6b3f14d10f322de3263a9c57","tid":2441593,"uid":45123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:01:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭有撚理過呢啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢只係識奶共"},{"pid":"7aed034c42fb04be4821bcc3b1598ba6a8d517a1","tid":2441593,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9ee7125e4fcacbb6b3f14d10f322de3263a9c57","tid":2441593,"uid":45123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:01:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭有撚理過呢啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢只係識奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:03:57.000Z","msg":"佢唔係玩加税？"},{"pid":"6dbe0cede89c3966d196b1071b5eacf0b8078088","tid":2441593,"uid":63287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:39:55.000Z","msg":"打咁多字多餘<br />\n<br />\n一個字<br />\n<br />\n升！"},{"pid":"3ab5a